Package: gpxtoolbox
Title: Tools for Analyzing and Visualizing GPX Files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Martin", "Chan", , "martinchan53@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides functions for processing, analyzing, and visualizing GPS track data
    from GPX files. The package offers tools for calculating route metrics such as 
    distance, elevation gain/loss, and speed, as well as visualization capabilities
    for elevation profiles and route maps. Designed for outdoor enthusiasts, athletes,
    and researchers who work with GPS tracking data.
